            <thetext>If a doc comment contains two or more &lt;pre&gt; HTML elements and the second one contains only the number 0, e.g.:

/**
 * &lt;pre&gt;Foo&lt;/pre&gt;
 * &lt;pre&gt;0&lt;/pre&gt;
 */

textile will replace the content of the first element with [[[[[REPL0]]]]]

Since our textile version is fairly old, we might look into upgrading it.</thetext>
